775	  /**
776	   * Buffer an orphan-turn message chunk and (re)arm the quiescence timer.
777	   * Each new chunk pushes the flush out by orphanFlushQuiescenceMs so a
778	   * multi-chunk background summary is delivered as one message once the
779	   * agent goes quiet. No-op if the flusher is disabled (quiescence 0).
