901	   * A "substantive" close (>= config.archiveMinTurns turns with some assistant
902	   * output) is exported — including a close-time LLM summary — and saved. A
903	   * trivial close does NOT overwrite a more-substantive prior archive: the
904	   * stashed priorArchive is re-saved so the real work's context survives to the
