3	 *
4	 * Architecture:
5	 *   sendRelay(msg) -> transport switch:
6	 *     "redis"    -> LPUSH to Redis list "relay:<targetBot>"
7	 *     "telegram" -> bot.api.sendMessage(@targetBotUsername, text)
8	 *     "both"     -> telegram first, redis as fallback
9	 *   + sendMessage to group (mirror)
